      {
        "block_label": "text",
        "block_content": "We tabulated the default training parameters for the unconditional diffusion model on CIFAR-10 and ImageNet, and for Imagen on MS COCO, in Table 3. Given that we have employed ASR (Accuracy) as our evaluation metric, we endeavor to maintain a balance between the quantities of the member set and the non-member set to ensure the precision of model validation. The structure for the unconditional diffusion model aligns with those from the diffusers library [60] in Huggingface. Imagen is based on the open-source implementation by Phil Wang et al. $ ^{3} $, and we have retained consistency in its configuration. All experiments were conducted using two NVIDIA A100 GPUs.",
