      {
        "block_label": "text",
        "block_content": "In the process of comparing experimental results, we employ Attack Success Rate (ASR) [6], Area Under the ROC Curve (AUC), and True-Positive Rate (TPR) values under fixed low False-Positive Rate (FPR) as evaluation metrics.",
        "block_bbox": [
